reviewText: So you feel like YOU should have been a cowboy? Hey, not everybody has to be if they want to own a tape like this one. This tape has wonderful action and great music, including the song by Toby Keith, "Should have been a cowboy." Still, don't feel you must be a cowboy to love this. I don't feel that way whenever seeing this. But any action fan would be greatly moved by this entertaining program. Your cowboy friends might like it a lot too. Buy this tape!!!
